  <Method>
    <Step image="Baked%20Beans_bkb2.jpg">Presoak beans.</Step>
    <Step image="Baked%20Beans_caronion.jpg">Caramelize onions in a heavy skillet in the fat from the bacon.</Step>
    <Step image="Baked%20Beans_bkb5.jpg">Add the bacon to the onions to reheat it.</Step>
    <Step image="">Add the beans to a oven safe lidded casserole.</Step>
    <Step image="">Add 4 cups of water, and stir in all of the other ingredients.</Step>
    <Step image="Baked%20Beans_bkb7.jpg">Cook in the oven for 6 hours.</Step>
  </Method>
  <Variations>
    <Variation>This can also be made in a crock pot.</Variation>
  </Variations>
